ype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01825">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 20. 1. 1909</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01828">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 26. 1. 1909</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
